Sering kali tak sadar aku asyik dengan duniaku sendiri. Berjalan dengan congkak. Meremehkan yang kecil seolah apa yang mereka tahu tak sebanyak yang kutahu. Menertawakan yang tua karena kerentaan mereka. Saat langkahku kian jauh, saat kutemui ragam manusia yang lebih banyak di luar sana. Rasanya aku tertampar hingga sadar. Si muda yang aku remehkan, mengetahui lebih dari yang kutahu, dan si tua yang renta itu mempunyai semangat yang melebihi semangat mudaku. Lalu aku tertunduk malu sejadi-jadinya, berkata hatiku, apa yang kulakukan selama ini? Hanya berbaring dan merangkai cerita dalam anganku sendiri.

Don't mean to boast or show off. I share these pictures bcs I care. I deeply hope that everyone will realize about how important to keep ourselves and our living area clean. These pictures were taken in Bromo National Park. My friends and I were collecting a bunch of trashes there. Actually we were just collected ours. But something opened up our hearts. We finally collected trashes all along the way back to where our motorbike parked. Bromo was such a great place with its magnificence, but STILL there were few people there doing irresponsibility things. The real example was LITTERING. I saw Bromo as a real beautiful place from the distance and I was amazed. But when I strolled around there, I was so surprised with the "trashes view" Please guys, keep your litter home! Don't littering EVERYWHERE! Especially in public area. Next step is please put trashes on the right place though they are not yours. Lets do something eventhough only a small thing and I think it will be meaningful¬† to our environment. I hope that I can do something more than this.
